-fischer/|title=Sam Fischer {{!}} full Official Chart history|publisher=[[Official Charts Company]]|accessdate=7 March 2020}}</ref>\n|-\n! scope=\"row\"| \"Lean\"\n| 2016\n| \u2014 || \u2014 || \u2014\n| rowspan=\"2\" {{n/a|non album singles}}\n|-\n! scope=\"row\"| \"Same Friends\"<ref>{{cite web|url= https://music.apple.com/au/album/same-friends-single/1302567680|title=Same Friends - Single|website=Apple Music|date=10 November 2017|accessdate=1 March 2020}}</ref>\n| rowspan=\"2\"| 2017\n| \u2014 || \u2014 || \u2014\n|-\n! scope=\"row\"| \"Getting Older\"<ref>{{cite web|url= https://music.apple.com/au/album/same-friends-single/1302567680|title=Getting Older - Single|website=Apple Music|date=28 November 2017|accessdate=1 March 2020}}</ref>\n| \u2014 || \u2014 || \u2014\n| rowspan=\"3\"|''Not a Hobby''\n|-\n! scope=\"row\"| \"Smoke\"<ref>{{cite web|url= https://music.apple.com/au/album/smoke-single/1332917573|title=Smoke - Single|website=Apple Music|date=11 January 2018|accessdate=1 March 2020}}</ref>\n| rowspan=\"4\"| 2018\n| \u2014 || \u2014 || \u2014\n|-\n! scope=\"row\"| \"[[This City (Sam Fischer song)|This City]]\"<ref>{{cite web|url=https://www.facebook.com/samfischermusic/videos/this-city-is-out-everywhere-but-spotify-right-now-but-were-working-on-it-%EF%B8%8F%EF%B8%8Fi-wro/1535664703136839/|title=\"This City\" Is Out|website=[[Facebook]]|date=18 January 2018|accessdate=4 April 2020}}</ref> \n| \u2014 || \u2014 || \u2014\n|-\n! scope=\"row\"| \"Restless\"<br />{{small|(with The Gifted)}}<ref>{{cite web|url=https://music.apple.com/au/album/restless-single/1417874146|title=Restless - Single|website=Apple Music|date=10 August 2018|accessdate=1 March 2020}}</ref>\n| \u2014 || \u2014 || \u2014\n| rowspan=\"2\" {{n/a|non album singles}}\n|-\n! scope=\"row\"| \"We Won't Back Down\"<br />{{small|(with Dirtier Blonde)}}<ref>{{cite web|url=https://music.apple.com/au/album/we-wont-back-down-single/1437204119|title=We Won't Back Down - Single|website=Apple Music|date=28 September 2018|accessdate=1 March 2020}}</ref>\n| \u2014 || \u2014 || \u2014\n|-\n! scope=\"row\"| \"This City\" {{small|(re-release)}}<ref>{{cite web|url=https://music.apple.com/au/album/smoke-single/1332917573|title=This City - Single|website=Apple Music|date=13 December 2019|accessdate=1 March 2020}}</ref>\n| 2019\n| \u2014{{efn|group=upper-alpha|\"This City\" did not enter the Australia ([[ARIA Charts]]) top 50, but peaked at number 8 on the Australian Artist Singles Chart.<ref name=\"13Apr20\">{{cite web|url=http://cdn.aria.com.au/pdfs/2FCAB7CA836D3EDE9F269863D8D40B95F988E96FD99682B5262F650135DFB2B1/ARIA%20Australian%20Artist%20Singles%20Chart.pdf?seq=31|title=ARIA Australian Artist Singles Chart|publisher=[[ARIA]]|date=13 April 2020|accessdate=16 April 2020}}</ref>}} || 41 || 39\n| ''Not a Hobby''\n|}\n\n====As featured artist====\n{| class=\"wikitable plainrowheaders\" style=\"text-align:center\"\n|-\n! scope=\"col\" rowspan=\"1\" style=\"width:16em;\"| Title\n! scope=\"col\" rowspan=\"1\"| Year\n! scope=\"col\" rowspan=\"1\"| Album\n|-\n! scope=\"row\"| \"Heartbeats\" <br>{{small|(Alex Preston featuring Sam Fischer)}}<ref name=\"heartbeats\">{{cite web|url=https://music.apple.com/au/album/heartbeat-feat-sam-fischer-single/541654662|title=Heartbeats|website=Apple Music|date= July 2012|accessdate=1 March 2020}}</ref>\n|2012\n|{{n/a|non album single}}\n|-\n! scope=\"row\"| \"Secrets\" <br>{{small|(Opia featuring Sam Fischer)}}<ref>{{cite web|url=https://music.apple.com/au/album/secrets-feat-sam-fischer-single/1223549679|title=Secrets (featuring Sam Fischer)|website=Apple Music|date=19 April 2017|accessdate=1 March 2020}}</ref>\n|2017\n|''Faded''\n|-\n! scope=\"row\"| \"Everybody Wants You\" <br>{{small|(Black Saint featuring Sam Fischer)}}<ref>{{cite web|url=https://music.apple.com/au/album/secrets-feat-sam-fischer-single/1223549679|title=Secrets (Black Saint featuring Sam Fischer)|website=Apple Music|date=25 January 2019|accessdate=1 March 2020}}</ref>\n| 2019\